'''-{zh-tw:喬納森;zh-hk:約拿單;zh-cn:乔纳森;}-·亞當·桑德斯·“傑”·巴魯契'''（{{lang-en|'''Jonathan Adam Saunders "Jay" Baruchel'''}}，{{bd|1982年|4月9日}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]][[演員|演員]]。他在[[喜劇電影|喜劇電影]]類型較為有突出表現，以及票房賣座的成績，代表作有《[[登峰造擊|登峰造擊]]》、《[[開麥拉驚魂|開麥拉驚魂]]》；近期知名作品有替[[夢工廠|夢工廠]]動畫《[[馴龍高手|-{zh-hk:馴龍記; zh-tw:馴龍高手; zh-cn:驯龙高手;}-]]》配音，與[[尼可拉斯·凱吉|尼可拉斯·凱吉]]合作主演的[[奇幻作品|奇幻]]魔法電影《[[魔法師的學徒|魔法師的學徒]]》。

==個人生平==
傑·巴魯契生於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]]的[[渥太華|渥太華]]，母親是自由作家，父親是[[古董|古董]]商。<ref name="peopleref">{{cite news|last=|first=|coauthors=|title=Quick Study|pages=|publisher=People|date=2001-11-12|url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20135700,00.html|accessdate=2010-03-12|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303205901/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20135700,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cinemablend">{{cite news|last=Rich|first=Katey|coauthors=|title=Interview: Jay Baruchel On Why He Won't Do Nude Scenes|pages=|publisher=Cinemablend|date=2010-03-10|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Interview-Jay-Baruchel-On-Why-He-Won-t-Do-Nude-Scenes-17488.html|accessdate=2010-03-13|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205010209/https://www.cinemablend.com/new/Interview-Jay-Baruchel-On-Why-He-Won-t-Do-Nude-Scenes-17488.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他早年都在[[蒙特婁|蒙特婁]][[魁北克|魁北克]]的社區成長，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://montrealfilmjournal.com/article.asp?A=A0000208 |title=JAY BARUCHEL: CANADA'S PROUDEST SON |accessdate=2009-09-14 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920024550/https://montrealfilmjournal.com/article.asp?A=A0000208 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和他的妹妹泰勒同住。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1807480083/bio|title=Jay Baruchel Biography|publisher=''[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]] Movies''|accessdate=2007-11-10|archive-date=2008-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080212164516/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1807480083/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref>他父親一半[[塞法迪猶太人|塞法迪猶太人]]，一半[[法裔加拿大人|法裔加拿大人]]，母親是[[愛爾蘭天主教|愛爾蘭天主教]]。<ref name=magnow>{{cite news|last=Simonpillai|first=Radheyan|coauthors=|title=Jay Baruchel is the Trotsky|pages=|publisher=NOW Magazine|date=2010-05-13|url=http://www.nowtoronto.com/movies/story.cfm?content=174991|accessdate=2010-05-13|quote=The funny thing is, Baruchel is only a quarter Jewish... His background is also French and Irish-Catholic... He may be hard to identify ethnically...|archive-date=2014-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407033012/http://www.nowtoronto.com/movies/story.cfm?content=174991|dead-url=no}}</ref>他說本身是個「純粹的[[不可知論|不可知論]]者」。<ref name="ref13">{{cite news|last=McLeod|first=Andre|coauthors=|title=Jay Baruchel: Breaking Out|pages=|publisher=Complex|date=2008|url=http://www.complex.com/STYLE/Style-Features/Jay-Baruchel-Breaking-Out?page=5|accessdate=2010-03-12}}</ref><ref name="ref081">{{cite news|last=|first=|coauthors=|title=Montreal actor improvising his way to the top|pages=|publisher=Canada.com|date=2008-01-03|url=http://www.canada.com/topics/entertainment/story.html?id=3fa5a01f-2c30-4cf3-b9dd-dfd2f1d3582f|accessdate=2010-03-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080529012419/http://www.canada.com/topics/entertainment/story.html?id=3fa5a01f-2c30-4cf3-b9dd-dfd2f1d3582f|archivedate=2008-05-29}}</ref>

巴魯契是個[[蒙特利爾加拿大人|蒙特利爾加拿大人]]隊的大粉絲。身上有多個[[刺青|刺青]]：在他的右手臂有個[[凱爾特十字|凱爾特十字]]<ref name=3vt>{{cite news|last=|first=|coauthors=|title=Celebrity Interview: Jay Baruchel|pages=|publisher=TV3|date=2010-04-07|url=http://www.tv3.ie/article.php?article_id=35310&locID=1.65.68.269&pagename=|accessdate=2010-07-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314040831/http://www.tv3.ie/article.php?article_id=35310&locID=1.65.68.269&pagename=|archivedate=2012-03-14}}</ref>，前臂有他母親的娘家姓，左胸有個[[楓葉|楓葉]]，在電影《[[好孕臨門|-{zh-cn:一夜大肚; zh-tw:好孕臨門; zh-hk:弊傢伙…搞大咗;}-]]》可被看見。<ref name=uqra>{{cite news|last=Farquharson|first=Vanessa|coauthors=|title=The Trotsky's Jay Baruchel: On moviemaking, microphones and mom tattoos|pages=|publisher=The National Post|date=2010-05-11|url=http://www.nationalpost.com/story.html?id=3014493|accessdate=2010-07-15}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

